title: ITV Tour De France 2011 Stage 17 Highlights (20th July 2011) PDT

ITV Tour De France 2011 Stage 17 Highlights (20th July 2011) PDTV x264 AAC

Presented by Gary Imlach, Chris Boardman and Ned Boulting. Highlights of Stage 17 - Gap to Pinerolo - 179km. The riders race between twinned towns and enter Italy, the only country outside of France hosting a stage of this year's Tour. This is not a pure climbers stage but do not expect to see the sprinters at the finish. Commentary: Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen.
